                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>** <hi rend="italic">to having been convicted at this Court in February</hi>,1876, <hi rend="italic">in the name of Ellen Blown, of uttering counter<lb></lb>feit coin</hi>,—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18800628-444-punishment-56" type="punishmentDescription">
